📍 Where is App Development Used?

App Development plays a key role across industries:
	•	Banking & Finance:
Apps like Google Pay, Paytm, and PhonePe enable secure online payments and transactions.
	•	Social Media:
Platforms like Instagram, Snapchat, and WhatsApp allow global communication and content sharing.
	•	Healthcare:
Apps such as Practo and Apollo 24/7 help users book doctor appointments, store medical records, and order medicines.
	•	E-commerce:
Apps like Amazon and Flipkart revolutionized shopping by making it online, easy, and fast.
	•	Education:
Learning platforms like Byju’s, Coursera, and Udemy make knowledge accessible to all.
	•	Entertainment:
Netflix, Spotify, and YouTube bring personalized content to your screen.

